<sect1 id="dir_65d165468c717c67bace063bdb86ff73_1autotoc_md252">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::match</title><para>Match state management for the helios engine.</para>
<para>This module provides domain-specific types and bindings for managing match states (Warmup, PlayerSpawn, Playing). It uses the generic <computeroutput><ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1engine_1_1state" kindref="compound">helios::engine::state</ref></computeroutput> framework.</para>
</sect1>
