<sect1 id="dir_65d165468c717c67bace063bdb86ff73_1autotoc_md255">
<title>Architecture</title><para><computeroutput>MatchStateManager</computeroutput> is a type alias for <computeroutput>StateManager&lt;MatchState&gt;</computeroutput>:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">using<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1match_1a151fc4e8d8a8f2eb87866789883eda39" kindref="member">MatchStateManager</ref><sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1state_1_1StateManager" kindref="compound">helios::engine::state::StateManager&lt;types::MatchState&gt;</ref>;</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>The generic <computeroutput>StateManager</computeroutput> provides:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Rule-based transitions with optional guards</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Listener notifications on state changes</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Command-driven state changes via <computeroutput>StateCommand&lt;MatchState&gt;</computeroutput></para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
